---
title: Hot Honey Pork Filet with Roasted Sesame Carrots & Cilantro Lime Rice
description: Dreaming about dinner? How about succulent pork filet, roasted sesame carrots, and fluffy cilantro lime rice? To finish things off, the pork is drizzled in a lick-the-plate-worthy sauce made with sesame oil, scallions, ginger, and honey. Talk about a dream come true!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6655f1c08a4eed4f27b52f6e-772f5c06.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6655f1c08a4eed4f27b52f6e-en-US.pdf
